A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to public health and safety; authorizing
2 the use of autologous or direct blood donations as
3 specified; authorizing reasonable fees for blood donations;
4 providing definitions; requiring rulemaking; and providing
5 for effective dates.
6
7 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
8
9 Section 1. W.S. 35-34-101 is created to read:
